task: Verify ClusterMap static import fix is complete and clean
status: done

context: |
  react-leaflet-markercluster was wrapped in React.lazy() which caused
  "TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'include')"
  because the library calls L.SomeClass.include({}) at module init time.
  Lazy/async loading means Leaflet's class chain may not be ready at that point.

  Fix applied in branch qf-18032026:
  - Removed: lazy(() => import('react-leaflet-markercluster')) + Suspense wrapper
  - Added: import MarkerClusterGroup from 'react-leaflet-markercluster'
  - Static import = bundled synchronously = init order guaranteed

done:
  - Static import replaces lazy() in ClusterMap.tsx
  - Suspense wrapper removed from JSX
  - tsc --noEmit exits 0

out: [src-client/src/features/map/ClusterMap.tsx]
